<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Privacy Policy — Nevarro Technologies</title>
<style>
  :root{--bg:#fbfbfd;--text:#1d1d1f;--muted:#6e6e73;--faint:#a1a1a6;--hairline:#e8e8ed;--accent:#5e8bff}
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark){
    :root{--bg:#0d0d10;--text:#f5f5f7;--muted:#a1a1a6;--faint:#6e6e73;--hairline:#2a2a30;--accent:#7da2ff}
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"SF Pro Text","Helvetica Neue",Inter,Arial,sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:1.2rem clamp(1.5rem,5vw,4rem)}
  .wordmark{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none}
  nav a{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none}
  main{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem 5rem}
  h1{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  .updated{color:var(--faint);font-size:.85rem;margin-top:.6rem}
  h2{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;margin:2.2rem 0 .6rem}
  p,li{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;font-size:.96rem}
  ul{padding-left:1.2rem;margin:.4rem 0}
  a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--hairline);text-align:center;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--faint);padding:1.2rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav><a class="wordmark" href="/">NEVARRO</a><a href="/">← Home</a></nav>
<main>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

  <h2>1. What we collect</h2>
  <p>When you contact us or purchase a product or engagement, we collect the information you provide: your name, email address, company details, and the content of your communications. Our payment partners collect payment information directly; we never see or store your card, bank, or UPI details.</p>

  <h2>2. How we use it</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to enquiries and deliver products and engagements you've purchased</li>
    <li>To send invoices, receipts, and service communications</li>
    <li>To comply with legal, tax, and accounting obligations</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not sell your data, and we do not send marketing email without your consent.</p>

  <h2>3. Payment processing</h2>
  <p>Payments are processed by third-party payment partners (which may act as merchant of record). Their handling of your payment data is governed by their own privacy policies, presented at checkout.</p>

  <h2>4. Cookies and analytics</h2>
  <p>This is a static website and does not use advertising cookies. If we use privacy-respecting analytics, they collect aggregate usage data only. Our free tools may be hosted on third-party platforms with their own privacy terms.</p>

  <h2>5. Data retention</h2>
  <p>We retain engagement records and correspondence for as long as needed to provide services and meet legal obligations (typically up to 8 years for financial records under Indian law), after which they are deleted.</p>

  <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by writing to us. We comply with applicable data protection law, including India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>Privacy questions: <a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com">support@nevarrotech.com</a></p>
</main>
<footer>© 2026 Nevarro Technologies · <a href="/terms">Terms</a> · <a href="/support">Support</a></footer>
</body>
</html>
